	<h1 class='text-20 text-word-2 mb-8'>Position</h1>
	<h2 class='font-light text-word-3 mb-24'>Utilities for controlling how an
		element is positioned in the DOM.
	</h2>

	<details class='font-light text-word-4 list-none mb-16'>
		<p>You can also use the breakpoint modifier to apply the class at only a
			specific screen size and above. Example:
			md-{static|fixed|absolute|relative|sticky}
		</p>
	</details>

